---
title: Grilled Hawaiian Shoyu-Style Chicken Breasts  with Fluffy Rice and Foil-Pouch Veggies
description: Hawaiian shoyu chicken is island-style comfort food! Simmer chicken breasts in a flavourful mix of soy, mirin, brown sugar, ginger and garlic! Once cooked through, grill and baste the chicken with its braising liquid! Want to prep ahead? Braise the chicken ahead of time, cool and refrigerate, then reheat on the grill when you're ready to serve!
